<paragraph id="A9BA7921CCBB2C4C89B6BDDE45085569" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
It has to be noted that we had problems in identifying 
<emphasis id="CE74225FD39AD8C019B9E37A251EC61F" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<normalizedToken id="44CEDCB1095E592B54FA46766EE37EFC" originalValue="Beltrán">Beltran</normalizedToken>
7987
</emphasis>
(USM). This specimen exhibits the characteristic flat and ciliate leaves of 
<taxonomicName id="06E0F8C35C3D8D51C93B8D97CBA42C26" genus="X." lsidName="X. decorum" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="species" species="decorum">
